data.description: this great 2 story 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath, 1 car garage townhome located at the end of the road in a vibrant community of Marbella on Cypress! This home comes complete with soaring ceilings cased in crown molding, 18" ceramic tile set on the diagonal downstairs. This great room floorplan is perfect sized for a growing family with over 1900 sq ft under air conditioning. Master bedroom features 2 separate walk in closets, a spacious master bathroom features a tiled up shower and dual sinks with upgraded lighting. Marbella on Cypress is a gated pet-friendly community with outstanding amenities, a resort style pool, movie theater, clubhouse, LOW HOA FEES, and NO CDD. With a location near shopping, restaurants, and groceries, SWFL International airport, and the Fort Myers River District. Do not miss your opportunity to own in this great place.
